# Graphical Description of Immunogenicity Data {#immuno_graphical}

## Pairs plots

```{r immuno-graphical-setup, echo = FALSE, message = FALSE}
library(here)
library(latex2exp)

here::i_am("immuno-graphical/report.Rmd")

## define study name
study_name = "mock"
```

```{r, fig.cap = "(Mock data) Pairs plots of D1 Ab markers: baseline negative vaccine + placebo arms"}
    knitr::include_graphics(here::here("immuno_graphical", "figs", "pairs_baselineMarkers_BaselineNeg_", study_name, ".png"))
```
